---
title: Chicken Souvlaki Pita Pockets with Tzatziki and Turkish-Spiced Sweet Potatoes
description: Simple, convenient, and delicious: that’s what’s in store with our Chicken Souvlaki Pita Pockets recipe, made with pre-measured, high-quality ingredients.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-souvlaki-pita-pockets-366cae3c.jpg
